kawa: Kawa is a general-purpose programming language that runs on the Java
kawa: platform.
kawa: 
kawa: It is an extension of the long-established Scheme language, which is
kawa: in the Lisp family of programming languages. Kawa has many useful
kawa: features.
kawa: Kawa is also a useful framework for implementing other programming
kawa: languages on the Java platform. It has many useful utility classes. 
kawa:
kawa: https://www.gnu.org/software/kawa/
kawa:
